LAGOS – Nollywood actress, Laide Bakare, has revealed the secret to her success after purchasing her latest Benz vehicle last week. She disclosed this via her Instagram page, stating that she would be releasing her latest book titled ‘How To Get Super Rich In 6 Months’, to show that the secret to her success is preparation, hardworking and learning from her failures. The actress wrote, “My BOOK, HOW TO GET SUPER RICH IN 6 MONTHS IS COMING SOON. How can you call it show off, when I haven’t even told you I just got this NEW Benz last week. -Advertisement- “There is no secret to my success, its the result of PREPARATIONS. HARD WORK AND learning from my failure. MUCH EFFORT MUCH PROSPERITY. “I REPEAT. my sweat, MY MONEY, my Reward , my pride , my home my happiness. If you think p**zy can get you all these Achievements haaa!!! omo!!! The Area go just expand in vein ni, so stop lying to the public, ME ke?  ME wey be say, na paiko i dey, even presently I DO NOT HAVE A BOYFRIEND, My focus is majorly on my Business and my children.” Recall that the actress on May 3, 2022, bought two cars at the same time, a few weeks after her house opening in April 2022.